{
  "stem": "23572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, Pavarotti comes from Modena, so that's his hometown.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's near-- it's near-- not-- not too far from Bologna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bologna is better known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this is Pavarotti's hometown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrive in this village, which is about, I would say, maybe 15 miles away from-- from Modena.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We see practically the whole village is at the railroad station, you know, with the-- they only had two policeman, three policemen, you know, the chief of police, he was called the [? carabinieri ?], which is the militia.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole village-- so we-- we were wondering, why, what's this-- what's this big welcome?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found out later on that the village came-- they had never seen a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The word came around in this little-- little village that Jews are coming, just like like-- like saying-- saying like, we are gonna have people from Mars coming.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had never seen a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This whole village came to the railroad station to look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They figured, maybe we have horns, maybe-- I don't know-- OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- that's the stories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now we are in Nonantola, and again, we are setting up [? hashara. ?] In the meantime, we get other-- other people are joining us from other-- we had some Yugoslavian kids.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The group, almost-- from 30, we almost were 100 setting up shop in-- in this-- in this place, in Nonantola.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "According to the law, we were-- we were not supposed to leave the city, the village, but all we had to do is go to the chief of police and tell them that we wanted to go into town, which was Modena.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which was, Modena was the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
